  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The next time you hit a creature with a melee or ranged weapon or unarmed attack before this jutsu ends, you inject chakra into your enemy's muscles attempting to restrict their movements. The target must make a Strength saving throw or be restrained until the end of their next turn. A large or larger creature has advantage on the saving throw. While restrained by this jutsu, the target takes 1d8 poison damage at the start of each of its turns.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d8</p>",
